            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>In 2026 I will be 62 years old. I have today 4 children. {name} is 28 years old,  {name} is 26, {name} is 24 an {name} 23. In 10 years time {name} and {name} will get engaged.{name} will have with her husband {name} two children and {name} will work abroad. So I will like to spoil my grandchildren during the week-end because I will still work. The age of pension will be relayed because of a lack of money at the Belgian Financial Ministery.</p>
            </div>
